{"id": "1413087055050969088", "channel_id": "1413087055050969088", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "《艺术娱报》，只报猛料。\n\n读者朋友们，你们是否思考过“真实与虚假”的问题：我们所看见的世界是真实的吗？\n\n🖼️皮克曼先生宣扬自己的画有“进入真实”的魔力，他的同学██曾亲身见证：\n*“食客交杯换盏，钻入胃袋大肆朵颐一番；\n血肉酣畅蠕动，腥腐的陈酿正释放醇香；\n世界浓墨重彩，每一幅面孔都狰狞绮丽。”*\n……这畸形的世界本质……\n\n小编为各位读者朋友争取到了几个珍贵的入画名额，机会难得，不要错过~\n☎️**报名热线：**▼▼▼▼▼\n💰️**报名费用：**限时折扣299坊\n\n——✦——✦—— ✦✦✦ ——✦——✦——\n\nArt & Scandal Gazette，we only break the big ones.\n\nDear readers, have you ever pondered the question of \"truth and falsehood\": Is the world we see real?\n\n🖼️Mr. Pickman proclaims that his paintings possess the magic of \"entering the truth,\" and his classmate ██ has witnessed it firsthand:\n*\"Guests clink glasses and exchange cups, indulging heartily in the feast.\nThe flesh writhes in ecstasy, and the stench of corruption from the aged brew releases a rich aroma;\nThe world is painted in vivid colors, each face is both grotesque and magnificent.\"*\n...the essence of this distorted world...\n\nThe editor has secured a few precious spots for readers to enter the painting event. This is a rare opportunity, so don't miss out~\n☎️**Registration Hotline:** ▼▼▼▼▼\n💰️**Registration Fee:** Limited-Time Discount of 299 Florin", "timestamp": "2025-09-04T09:03:27.812000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-04T09:09:23.924000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Cheerup", "emoji_id": "1400771555939844149", "count": 38}, {"emoji": "pray", "emoji_id": "1400771650064089112", "count": 24}, {"emoji": "zoomies", "emoji_id": "1351017471569694842", "count": 5}, {"emoji": "gogogo", "emoji_id": "1356053074560422118", "count": 2}, {"emoji": "wow", "emoji_id": "1356053147029864518", "count": 2}, {"emoji": "behave", "emoji_id": "1361909598067625984", "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1413087055688237066", "filename": "logo.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2785440, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1413087055050969088/1413087055688237066/logo.jpg?ex=69ccdf5f&is=69cb8ddf&hm=9d900c7559034db17d84ee34a722a3d5455260c182ba07607c25882bccf630a5&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1413087055050969088", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.3.2 皮克曼情报3：探访画中世界，名额有限先到先得┊About Pickman: Explore the world within the painting", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
